  "texts": [
    "The findings of this study can inform the creation of educational tools and resources that help individuals recognize and respond to misinformation, thereby fostering a more informed and discerning public.",
    "Overall, the theoretical advancements and practical applications of this study contribute to broader efforts to combat misinformation and promote a healthier information ecosystem.",
    "This study introduces a Hierarchical Graph-based Integration Network (H-GIN) that is specifically intended to identify propaganda in text within a certain topic using multilabel categorization.",
    "The H-GIN is used to construct a three-channel graph, consisting of the RDEP, ADMF, and final classifier.",
    "RDEP procedures specifically enable the exchange of information between remote nodes, whereas ADMF standardizes Three Channels, namely sequence, semantic, and syntactic information."
